value: south central Amazonian Brazil (between the Madeira and Tapajós rivers, south to the Aripuaña River)
Brazil south of the Amazon on the right bank of the lower Madeira (Borba) and the left bank of the lower Tapajoz (Villa Braga); known only from two females.
